# Auto-Build After Changes

After fixing a bug or implementing a feature in this IntelliJ plugin project, always run the Gradle build to produce the plugin zip:

```bash
./gradlew clean buildPlugin
```

This compiles, tests, and produces the distributable zip at `build/distributions/zide-intelliJ-plugin-{version}.zip`.

Run this as the final step before reporting completion to the user. If the build fails, fix the errors before finishing.
